1
00:00:09,423 --> 00:00:16,997
{\an1}<i>[laughing] At last! The world</i>
<i>of the Infinite Tsukuyomi is</i>
<i>now here! </i>

2
00:00:20,769 --> 00:00:21,503
{\an1}[inhaling sharply]

3
00:00:22,937 --> 00:00:24,205
[grunting]

4
00:00:24,239 --> 00:00:26,041
{\an1}Naruto, don't
move an inch.

5
00:00:26,074 --> 00:00:26,908
Huh?!

6
00:00:27,343 --> 00:00:29,111
{\an1}Hold on. Don't go outside.

7
00:00:29,145 --> 00:00:33,949
{\an1}<i>Without this Susano'o's</i>
<i>protection, you'd be bound</i>
<i>up in his genjutsu, too! </i>

8
00:02:16,063 --> 00:02:20,536
{\an7}"Itachi's Story - Light
and Darkness: Birth and
Death"

9
00:02:21,437 --> 00:02:23,906
{\an1}Whoa... What happened...?!

10
00:03:09,056 --> 00:03:11,191
What the-?!

11
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,961
<i>What is this? </i>

12
00:03:18,433 --> 00:03:20,168
{\an1}Are they in there?

13
00:03:20,435 --> 00:03:25,140
{\an1}The light isn't able to
penetrate that Susano'o?

14
00:03:27,443 --> 00:03:29,779
{\an1}So what's going on outside
right now?

15
00:03:32,047 --> 00:03:33,216
Well, Sasuke?

16
00:03:33,250 --> 00:03:35,418
{\an1}What difference
does it make to you?

17
00:03:35,452 --> 00:03:37,120
[grunting]

18
00:03:37,387 --> 00:03:40,223
{\an1}There's nothing that you can
do about it anyway.

19
00:03:40,257 --> 00:03:42,960
{\an1}Sasuke... That's not the
point.

20
00:03:42,994 --> 00:03:47,231
{\an1}Naruto and I also want to
know what's happening out
there.

21
00:03:47,265 --> 00:03:50,369
{\an1}In order to analyze our next
move, Sakura is--

22
00:03:50,402 --> 00:03:54,306
{\an1}Kakashi. You're being
just like Sakura right now.

23
00:03:54,339 --> 00:03:55,909
{\an1}Just be quiet for a bit.

24
00:03:55,942 --> 00:03:57,577
{\an1}<i>Hey, Sasuke! </i>

25
00:03:57,610 --> 00:04:01,247
{\an1}We're a team, and we need to
act like it! Team 7 has to
work together if we wanna

26
00:04:01,281 --> 00:04:02,715
{\an1}bring Madara down!

27
00:04:02,749 --> 00:04:05,251
{\an1}<i>You're right, there's</i>
<i>nothing I can do right</i>
<i>now... </i>

28
00:04:05,285 --> 00:04:07,555
{\an1}Huh?! Kakashi Sensei!

29
00:04:07,588 --> 00:04:12,560
{\an1}If you're able to analyze
what's outside with your
left eye, Sasuke...

30
00:04:12,593 --> 00:04:16,631
{\an1}...then you should be the
one to lead Team 7's
four-man squad.

31
00:04:16,665 --> 00:04:17,699
What?!

32
00:04:19,267 --> 00:04:22,103
{\an1}Do you seriously think he's
any better at strategizing
than you or Sakura?!

33
00:04:22,137 --> 00:04:24,239
I really
doubt it!

34
00:04:24,272 --> 00:04:26,074
{\an1}<i>Although he might be</i>
<i>better than me.</i>

35
00:04:26,642 --> 00:04:27,610
{\an1}Anyway...

36
00:04:27,978 --> 00:04:30,313
{\an1}<i>Madara has launched his</i>
<i>jutsu. </i>

37
00:04:30,346 --> 00:04:33,050
{\an1}<i>It's a powerful genjutsu. </i>

38
00:04:33,082 --> 00:04:37,588
{\an1}<i>And I suspect... that</i>
<i>everyone outside has fallen</i>
<i>under its spell. </i>

39
00:04:40,491 --> 00:04:42,360
{\an1}We four might be...

40
00:04:42,994 --> 00:04:45,030
{\an1}...the only ones unaffected.

41
00:04:47,231 --> 00:04:49,702
{\an1}The Infinite Tsukuyomi...

42
00:04:49,735 --> 00:04:52,103
{\an1}You mean... everybody is...?

43
00:04:52,871 --> 00:04:54,074
{\an1}[lightly gasping]

44
00:04:56,977 --> 00:04:58,979
{\an1}Trapped in a dream.

45
00:05:22,705 --> 00:05:24,073
<i>Lord Kiba! </i>

46
00:05:24,107 --> 00:05:25,508
<i>[cheering]</i>

47
00:05:25,541 --> 00:05:28,778
I'll start with
establishing a new holiday
called Dog Day!

48
00:05:29,245 --> 00:05:30,246
{\an1}[barking]

49
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:32,049
{\an1}Hokage's Decree!

50
00:05:32,082 --> 00:05:35,719
[cheering]

51
00:05:35,753 --> 00:05:38,355
{\an1}Everyone will own a dog!

52
00:05:38,389 --> 00:05:41,325
{\an1}Go get a dog! Hokage's
Decree!

53
00:05:41,358 --> 00:05:44,396
[cheering]

54
00:05:48,134 --> 00:05:51,269
{\an1}I've finally found
a new species!

55
00:05:51,302 --> 00:05:52,738
[laughing]

56
00:05:52,772 --> 00:05:56,943
There, there.
[laughing]

57
00:05:58,612 --> 00:06:00,414
<i>Wow! </i>

58
00:06:00,914 --> 00:06:03,517
{\an1}What a feast! So tasty!

59
00:06:03,550 --> 00:06:06,988
{\an1}I went all out and
cooked this up. Just
for you, dear!

60
00:06:07,021 --> 00:06:09,289
{\an1}It looks like you've
finally found a fan!

61
00:06:09,322 --> 00:06:11,659
{\an1}Thanks for the food!

62
00:06:11,693 --> 00:06:20,170
[eating]

63
00:06:20,202 --> 00:06:24,107
{\an1}Oh, I absolutely love
gluttons! They're
so sexy!

64
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:25,307
[realizing]

65
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:28,812
{\an1}I'm sorry. But I, uh,
ate your share, too.

66
00:06:28,845 --> 00:06:30,114
{\an1}It's okay!

67
00:06:30,147 --> 00:06:32,183
{\an1}'Cause there's still plenty
more!

68
00:06:33,851 --> 00:06:39,323
{\an1}Oooh! I am so happy!

69
00:06:40,758 --> 00:06:42,661
{\an1}<i>How many times do I have to</i>
<i>tell you?! </i>

70
00:06:42,694 --> 00:06:46,932
{\an1}If you're going to be late
coming back from a mission,
let me know!

71
00:06:46,965 --> 00:06:48,567
{\an1}I made dinner for nothing
'cause you weren't--

72
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:51,804
{\an1}Marriage is such a drag. I
think I'll pass.

73
00:06:52,705 --> 00:06:53,573
Yeah.

74
00:06:53,606 --> 00:06:55,374
{\an1}Mm.

75
00:06:57,945 --> 00:06:59,646
{\an1}<i>I won't let you have her! </i>

76
00:07:00,714 --> 00:07:03,183
{\an1}Ino is my girl! Now scram!

77
00:07:03,217 --> 00:07:05,586
{\an1}You're wrong! Ino is mine!

78
00:07:05,619 --> 00:07:08,455
Oh. Both of you.
Please don't fight!

79
00:07:09,124 --> 00:07:11,960
{\an1}She's so popular! That's
my girl!!

80
00:07:11,993 --> 00:07:15,530
This is just so
horrible! Oh no!
[giggling]

81
00:07:18,734 --> 00:07:21,170
{\an1}Great Leaf Hurricane!

82
00:07:22,037 --> 00:07:23,339
[grunting]

83
00:07:23,372 --> 00:07:25,208
[grunting]

84
00:07:25,242 --> 00:07:27,077
[groaning]

85
00:07:27,110 --> 00:07:28,912
{\an1}Yes! Youth prevails!

86
00:07:28,945 --> 00:07:30,347
{\an1}Oh, Lee!

87
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:31,648
[giggling]

88
00:07:31,681 --> 00:07:32,984
{\an1}I love you!

89
00:07:33,017 --> 00:07:35,219
Uh... S-Sakura!

90
00:07:37,287 --> 00:07:38,723
<i>Sai. Sai! </i>

91
00:07:39,724 --> 00:07:40,858
Huh? Oh, Sai!

92
00:07:40,892 --> 00:07:42,060
{\an1}Hey! Sai!

93
00:07:42,094 --> 00:07:43,561
{\an1}<i>Good morning, everyone! </i>

94
00:07:43,594 --> 00:07:44,897
Morning!

95
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:46,832
{\an1}You always have
such a nice smile.

96
00:07:46,865 --> 00:07:47,866
You think so?

97
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,969
{\an1}Yeah, you have a
beautiful smile!

98
00:07:50,003 --> 00:07:51,104
It is cool!

99
00:07:51,137 --> 00:07:51,905
Oh, yeah?

100
00:07:51,938 --> 00:07:53,973
{\an1}Sai! Your smile is...

101
00:07:54,007 --> 00:07:55,208
{\an1}...the best in the Hidden
Leaf!

102
00:07:55,241 --> 00:07:59,146
[laughing]

103
00:08:00,781 --> 00:08:02,983
{\an1}<i>I've finally perfected it!</i>

104
00:08:04,118 --> 00:08:09,958
{\an1}<i>It walks! It flies! It's my</i>
<i>ultimate puppet! It embodies</i>
<i>the Sand's dreams!</i>

105
00:08:09,991 --> 00:08:12,260
{\an1}<i>It'll be the guardian deity</i>
<i>of the Sand!</i>

106
00:08:12,294 --> 00:08:14,563
[roaring]

107
00:08:15,131 --> 00:08:18,000
[laughing]
C'mon, let's go!

108
00:08:25,108 --> 00:08:27,744
{\an1}<i>Elder Sister, Elder Sister! </i>

109
00:08:28,045 --> 00:08:31,949
{\an1}<i>Please help me. I need to</i>
<i>pick your brain about</i>
<i>something! </i>

110
00:08:31,982 --> 00:08:34,819
{\an1}Just calm down. And
what is it now?

111
00:08:34,853 --> 00:08:36,087
Well, you see-

112
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,823
{\an1}Hold on a second. Let
me discuss something
with you first!

113
00:08:38,857 --> 00:08:43,095
{\an1}Look, you're the Kazekage
now. Make your own
decisions!

114
00:08:43,128 --> 00:08:46,031
{\an1}No way! I really have to
hear your opinion!

115
00:08:46,065 --> 00:08:47,700
{\an1}Me, too! Please, Elder
Sister, help me!

116
00:08:47,733 --> 00:08:50,237
You're the only
one who can do it!

117
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,205
<i>Elder Sister! </i>

118
00:08:52,239 --> 00:08:53,505
[chuckling]

119
00:08:55,342 --> 00:08:58,279
{\an1}My little brothers are just
hopeless without me!

120
00:09:01,481 --> 00:09:09,757
[wedding bells]

121
00:09:11,126 --> 00:09:14,162
{\an1}<i>And get this! Then Gaara...!</i>

122
00:09:14,563 --> 00:09:16,665
{\an1}Is that so? At the Academy?

123
00:09:16,698 --> 00:09:17,900
Uh-huh!

124
00:09:17,934 --> 00:09:19,369
<i>Lord Gaara. </i>

125
00:09:19,401 --> 00:09:20,370
Huh?

126
00:09:20,402 --> 00:09:22,739
{\an1}Your friend has arrived.
He's here to see you.

127
00:09:23,439 --> 00:09:23,873
{\an1}<i>Hey! </i>

128
00:09:23,907 --> 00:09:25,142
[gasping]

129
00:09:25,175 --> 00:09:27,144
{\an1}So, what are we gonna play
today?

130
00:09:27,177 --> 00:09:28,544
{\an1}Let's go outside!

131
00:09:28,578 --> 00:09:29,380
Gaara!

132
00:09:29,412 --> 00:09:30,347
Uh!

133
00:09:31,682 --> 00:09:33,884
{\an1}Don't stay out too late.
[chuckling]

134
00:09:33,918 --> 00:09:34,885
Uh-huh!

135
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:36,720
Hee-hee.

136
00:09:36,754 --> 00:09:41,026
[laughing]

137
00:09:48,801 --> 00:09:50,169
{\an1}When can we get outta here?

138
00:09:50,404 --> 00:09:53,140
{\an1}The genjutsu seems to use
the moon's light.

139
00:09:53,806 --> 00:09:56,910
{\an1}And over time, that's
gradually going to wane.

140
00:09:56,944 --> 00:10:00,781
{\an1}But while there's still
light, it's useless.

141
00:10:01,416 --> 00:10:03,583
Damn it!

142
00:10:06,187 --> 00:10:11,327
{\an1}I must tell you everything
before I say goodbye and we
part for good.

143
00:10:12,695 --> 00:10:15,264
{\an1}There is no need to lie
anymore.

144
00:10:15,297 --> 00:10:18,600
I'll show you...
the entire truth.

145
00:10:23,273 --> 00:10:25,976
{\an1}<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>These are...</i>
<i>Itachi's memories.</i>

146
00:10:27,945 --> 00:10:31,615
{\an1}<i>Back then... Itachi told me</i>
<i>about the discord between</i>

147
00:10:31,649 --> 00:10:33,818
{\an1}<i>the Hidden Leaf</i>
<i>and the Uchiha.</i>

148
00:10:34,286 --> 00:10:36,587
{\an1}<i>But that wasn't all... </i>

149
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:40,459
{\an1}<i>Those weren't just</i>
<i>memories... It was</i>
<i>Itachi's knowledge.</i>

150
00:10:40,491 --> 00:10:43,296
{\an1}<i>His thoughts...</i>
<i>his suffering.</i>

151
00:10:45,365 --> 00:10:48,034
{\an1}No matter what, I will love
you always.

152
00:10:49,135 --> 00:10:51,871
{\an1}<i>It's everything that</i>
<i>Itachi Uchiha was.</i>

153
00:10:53,374 --> 00:10:57,644
{\an1}<i>Madara... don't you dare</i>
<i>talk about the Uchiha.</i>

154
00:10:57,678 --> 00:11:00,214
{\an1}<i>The only one who</i>
<i>has that right...</i>

155
00:11:00,448 --> 00:11:02,150
{\an1}<i>... is my big</i>
<i>brother.</i>

156
00:11:28,112 --> 00:11:40,558
<i>[yelling]</i>

157
00:11:40,591 --> 00:11:41,660
[grunting]

158
00:11:42,828 --> 00:11:44,531
[groaning]

159
00:11:49,669 --> 00:11:52,440
[grunting]

160
00:12:01,715 --> 00:12:07,422
[yelling]

161
00:12:07,456 --> 00:12:10,826
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>So this is... the</i>
<i>Great Ninja War.</i>

162
00:12:24,575 --> 00:12:27,579
[groaning]
Water... water!

163
00:12:27,611 --> 00:12:29,180
[panting]

164
00:12:29,214 --> 00:12:30,781
{\an1}[grunting]

165
00:12:30,814 --> 00:12:32,417
[grunting]

166
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:35,920
{\an1}[gulping]

167
00:12:36,321 --> 00:12:38,457
{\an1}Thanks for that...

168
00:12:38,957 --> 00:12:39,959
[gasping]

169
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,061
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>Ninja Tools? </i>

170
00:12:42,928 --> 00:12:43,996
[gasping]

171
00:12:46,665 --> 00:12:48,868
[yelling]

172
00:12:48,902 --> 00:12:53,441
{\an1}[groaning]

173
00:12:53,474 --> 00:12:54,941
Uh!

174
00:12:59,847 --> 00:13:04,553
{\an1}Father... I don't
understand. Why did this
shinobi try to kill me?

175
00:13:04,586 --> 00:13:06,221
{\an1}I didn't do anything!

176
00:13:06,721 --> 00:13:08,624
{\an1}Because this is war.

177
00:13:08,657 --> 00:13:10,359
{\an1}It's war...?

178
00:13:10,392 --> 00:13:14,663
{\an1}It's not a war between
people. It's a war between
nations.

179
00:13:15,165 --> 00:13:19,169
{\an1}That's why strangers kill
each other and do so
senselessly.

180
00:13:20,803 --> 00:13:22,540
{\an1}<i>That's what</i>
<i>war is?</i>

181
00:13:22,573 --> 00:13:24,674
It's what the
shinobi world is.

182
00:13:26,143 --> 00:13:29,648
{\an1}Listen, Itachi. Never
forget this sight.

183
00:13:32,450 --> 00:13:33,151
{\an1}<i>Hm.</i>

184
00:13:39,124 --> 00:13:42,795
{\an1}<i>We achieved a truce, but the</i>
<i>sacrifice was too great. </i>

185
00:13:43,663 --> 00:13:46,832
{\an1}<i>Lord Third will take full</i>
<i>responsibility and retire. </i>

186
00:13:47,534 --> 00:13:50,504
{\an1}<i>There's support for making</i>
<i>you Fourth Hokage. </i>

187
00:13:50,537 --> 00:13:51,071
{\an1}Please, sir-

188
00:13:51,104 --> 00:13:52,372
{\an1}Enough talk for now.

189
00:13:52,406 --> 00:13:53,340
{\an1}Hm.

190
00:13:54,308 --> 00:13:56,210
{\an1}<i>What should we do about</i>
<i>Kakashi Hatake? </i>

191
00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:57,978
Hmm.

192
00:13:59,614 --> 00:14:02,618
{\an1}<i>He doesn't belong to our</i>
<i>clan, but he possesses the</i>
<i>Sharingan. </i>

193
00:14:02,651 --> 00:14:07,855
{\an1}<i>I understand that Obito</i>
<i>Uchiha fought bravely. So</i>
<i>let's respect his wishes. </i>

194
00:14:08,857 --> 00:14:11,260
{\an1}<i>We should bring the</i>
<i>Sharingan back to the</i>
<i>Uchiha! </i>

195
00:14:11,561 --> 00:14:16,299
{\an7}The Great Ninja War has
just ended. Do not sow the
seeds of discord.

196
00:14:16,333 --> 00:14:17,801
{\an1}<i>Yes, sir. </i>

197
00:14:20,136 --> 00:14:24,976
{\an1}<i>We finally have peace. And</i>
<i>we must do our best to</i>
<i>maintain it. </i>

198
00:14:26,143 --> 00:14:29,146
{\an1}<i>That is the duty of the</i>
<i>Uchiha. </i>

199
00:14:30,449 --> 00:14:31,450
[gasping]

200
00:14:36,288 --> 00:14:40,627
{\an1}It is completely meaningless
to grieve over those who are
no longer living.

201
00:14:41,059 --> 00:14:45,832
{\an1}If there is any meaning in
death at all, it's to take
advantage of it.

202
00:14:47,701 --> 00:14:50,170
{\an1}So what's the meaning of
life, then?

203
00:14:50,204 --> 00:14:51,171
There is none.

204
00:14:51,205 --> 00:14:52,072
[sharp gasping]

205
00:14:53,374 --> 00:14:56,043
{\an1}The only way there is
meaning in life is if
it is eternal.

206
00:15:02,884 --> 00:15:05,353
Oh--hm?

207
00:15:16,633 --> 00:15:20,203
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>Life has...</i>
<i>no meaning.</i>

208
00:15:27,612 --> 00:15:28,747
{\an1}<i>[crow cawing]</i>

209
00:15:28,781 --> 00:15:29,881
[gasping]

210
00:15:30,516 --> 00:15:31,916
[grunting]

211
00:15:36,689 --> 00:15:37,489
[grunting]

212
00:15:38,223 --> 00:15:42,995
[grunting]

213
00:15:44,164 --> 00:15:45,532
[grunting]

214
00:16:09,592 --> 00:16:12,628
{\an1}There isn't really anyone
who wants to die, is there?

215
00:16:12,662 --> 00:16:14,163
[cawing]

216
00:16:15,865 --> 00:16:23,307
[cawing]

217
00:16:23,340 --> 00:16:24,375
{\an1}You guys.

218
00:16:24,409 --> 00:16:32,785
[cawing]

219
00:16:40,827 --> 00:16:42,962
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>What is life, anyway? </i>

220
00:16:49,069 --> 00:16:50,337
{\an1}Please take care.

221
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:51,672
{\an1}Yes, thank you!

222
00:16:52,139 --> 00:16:53,608
<i>Mom?</i>

223
00:16:53,641 --> 00:16:55,176
{\an1}<i>What is it, Itachi?</i>

224
00:16:55,643 --> 00:16:56,779
<i>Are you sick? </i>

225
00:16:57,145 --> 00:17:00,616
{\an1}Oh no. It's
nothing like that.

226
00:17:00,649 --> 00:17:01,617
{\an1}You see...

227
00:17:02,718 --> 00:17:05,822
{\an1}Soon now... you'll have a
little brother or sister.

228
00:17:05,855 --> 00:17:06,723
Huh?!

229
00:17:07,791 --> 00:17:12,295
{\an1}You heard right! You're
going to be a big brother.

230
00:17:14,799 --> 00:17:17,668
{\an1}<i>Mom,... I want it to be a</i>
<i>little brother. </i>

231
00:17:18,001 --> 00:17:20,871
{\an1}But a little sister would be
cute too, wouldn't she?

232
00:17:22,506 --> 00:17:24,074
{\an1}I bet it's a brother...

233
00:17:27,512 --> 00:17:29,915
{\an1}Oh, look!
Snow.

234
00:17:32,819 --> 00:17:35,421
{\an1}<i>The baby will be born</i>
<i>in the summer.</i>

235
00:17:36,823 --> 00:17:43,497
<i>[crying]</i>

236
00:17:43,530 --> 00:17:48,870
{\an1}[crying and whimpering]

237
00:17:48,903 --> 00:17:52,072
{\an1}It's a boy! Meet your
little brother.

238
00:17:52,407 --> 00:17:55,443
{\an1}[whimpering]

239
00:17:55,477 --> 00:17:58,546
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>A life. A new life.</i>

240
00:18:00,281 --> 00:18:01,316
Mmm.

241
00:18:01,349 --> 00:18:03,419
{\an1}Did you decide on a name?

242
00:18:03,452 --> 00:18:04,386
{\an1}Yes.

243
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:05,521
{\an1}He's Sasuke.

244
00:18:06,288 --> 00:18:08,157
{\an1}Sasuke Uchiha.

245
00:18:08,491 --> 00:18:11,828
{\an1}Oh. That's a fine name...
but it's...

246
00:18:11,862 --> 00:18:14,397
{\an1}Yes, it's the name of Lord
Third's father.

247
00:18:14,431 --> 00:18:17,467
{\an1}But I've already asked
Lord Third about it.

248
00:18:17,501 --> 00:18:18,636
I see.

249
00:18:19,570 --> 00:18:21,172
{\an1}Sasuke.

250
00:18:21,205 --> 00:18:23,574
{\an1}We'll raise him never
to dishonor his name.

251
00:18:25,142 --> 00:18:26,745
[laughing]

252
00:18:27,211 --> 00:18:27,946
[giggling]

253
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:29,180
There you go!

254
00:18:29,214 --> 00:18:30,449
{\an1}That's my boy, Itachi!

255
00:18:30,482 --> 00:18:33,018
{\an1}[laughing]
Itachi.

256
00:18:33,652 --> 00:18:34,787
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>I'm... </i>

257
00:18:35,488 --> 00:18:37,690
{\an1}<i>... like that, too. </i>

258
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:51,438
{\an1}<i>Birth... death...</i>
<i>birth... death...</i>

259
00:18:51,472 --> 00:18:53,374
{\an1}<i>Hey, there! </i>

260
00:18:53,842 --> 00:18:54,843
Hm?

261
00:18:55,510 --> 00:18:58,480
{\an1}You're Itachi Uchiha, right?
You're in my class!

262
00:18:58,513 --> 00:19:00,181
You wanna play?

263
00:19:00,215 --> 00:19:01,617
{\an1}So what do you
wanna do?

264
00:19:01,651 --> 00:19:04,620
{\an1}Kick the can! Let's play
kick the can!

265
00:19:04,654 --> 00:19:05,788
Huh?

266
00:19:05,821 --> 00:19:06,990
{\an1}But we just played that
yesterday!

267
00:19:07,024 --> 00:19:08,792
{\an1}Huh?

268
00:19:08,825 --> 00:19:09,559
Huh?

269
00:19:09,993 --> 00:19:12,563
{\an1}Hey! What, are you
dissing us?

270
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:15,165
{\an1}Say something!

271
00:19:16,667 --> 00:19:19,069
{\an1}I have shuriken training
now.

272
00:19:19,102 --> 00:19:20,471
Ooh!

273
00:19:20,505 --> 00:19:24,676
{\an1}All right, then... We should
get some shuriken practice
in, too!

274
00:19:24,709 --> 00:19:26,110
{\an1}No, guys, don't!

275
00:19:26,144 --> 00:19:26,946
[grunting]

276
00:19:28,146 --> 00:19:29,615
Whoa!

277
00:19:29,648 --> 00:19:30,516
That kid!

278
00:19:30,549 --> 00:19:33,352
{\an1}Trying to act cool!
Stuck up jerk!

279
00:19:33,385 --> 00:19:34,054
<i>[grunting]</i>

280
00:19:35,789 --> 00:19:39,124
{\an1}Come on! Please, you guys!
Enough! Stop it!

281
00:19:39,158 --> 00:19:43,430
{\an1}Shut up, Izumi! Stay out of
it. This is between us guys!

282
00:19:44,164 --> 00:19:45,700
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>Life is born. </i>

283
00:19:49,003 --> 00:19:50,638
<i>Life dies. </i>

284
00:19:52,673 --> 00:19:54,610
[grunting]

285
00:19:54,643 --> 00:19:57,446
<i>Life... is</i>
<i>a battle.</i>

286
00:19:57,913 --> 00:20:00,449
{\an1}Hey, come back! Don't
run away!

287
00:20:04,387 --> 00:20:05,421
[grunting]

288
00:20:14,064 --> 00:20:16,133
Wow!

289
00:20:16,166 --> 00:20:17,801
<i>You had a girl? </i>

290
00:20:17,836 --> 00:20:20,605
{\an1}[laughing]
No, he's a boy.

291
00:20:21,006 --> 00:20:22,641
{\an1}What a little cutie!

292
00:20:23,675 --> 00:20:25,276
{\an1}<i>What's your name, handsome? </i>

293
00:20:27,646 --> 00:20:30,616
[cooing]

294
00:20:30,650 --> 00:20:34,286
[cooing]

295
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:37,924
{\an1}<i>Hey Mom? Is Lord Fourth</i>
<i>going to have a baby, too? </i>

296
00:20:38,825 --> 00:20:41,228
{\an1}Yes! I wonder
what it'll be.

297
00:20:42,663 --> 00:20:45,298
{\an1}<i>I'll be going out tonight.</i>
<i>So, go ahead and have</i>
<i>dinner. </i>

298
00:20:46,934 --> 00:20:48,069
Okay.

299
00:20:48,335 --> 00:20:51,073
{\an1}<i>And your father's working,</i>
<i>so please watch Sasuke. </i>

300
00:20:51,572 --> 00:20:52,306
Sure.

301
00:21:07,824 --> 00:21:09,927
It's a full moon
tonight, Sasuke.

302
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:11,929
[whimpering]

303
00:21:11,962 --> 00:21:13,164
[chuckling]

304
00:21:15,198 --> 00:21:16,701
[gasping]

305
00:21:17,835 --> 00:21:20,538
[grunting]

306
00:21:20,772 --> 00:21:23,542
<i>What is this?</i>

307
00:22:59,015 --> 00:23:02,186
{\an1}<i>Welcome home, father!</i>
<i>Please, teach me a new</i>
<i>jutsu! </i>

308
00:23:02,219 --> 00:23:05,022
{\an1}A jutsu? Aren't they
teaching you at the Academy?

309
00:23:05,055 --> 00:23:06,455
{\an1}<i>Those are too easy. </i>

310
00:23:06,489 --> 00:23:09,026
{\an1}<i>[chuckling]</i>
<i>I guess they would</i>
<i>be, for you.</i>

311
00:23:09,059 --> 00:23:10,661
{\an1}<i>That's my</i>
<i>boy, Itachi.</i>

312
00:23:10,694 --> 00:23:12,729
{\an1}<i>Wait for me at</i>
<i>the training grounds.</i>

313
00:23:12,763 --> 00:23:14,833
{\an1}<i>Just make sure you're home</i>
<i>in time for dinner. </i>

314
00:23:16,333 --> 00:23:19,704
{\an1}<i>Next time on Naruto</i>
<i>Shippuden: "The Genius." </i>

315
00:23:20,338 --> 00:23:21,941
<i>Right! I got it.</i>

